products.title: SAMSUNG 970 PRO SSD 1TB - M.2 NVMe Interface Internal Solid State Drive with V-NAND Technology (MZ-V7P1T0BW) Black/Red
features: Built with Samsungs industry leading V-NAND technology for reliable and unrivaled performance
Seamless cloning and file transfers with the Samsung Magician Software, the ideal SSD management solution for performance optimization and data security with automatic firmware updates
Samsungs Dynamic Thermal Guard reduces risk of overheating and minimizes performance drops
The NVMe interface (PCIe M.2 2280) offers enhanced bandwidth, low latency, and power efficiency, perfect for tech enthusiasts, high-end gamers, and 4K & 3D content designers
compatible_devices: This drive is compatible with servers and arrays that accept M.2 2280 PCIe drives
products.description: Samsungs 970 PRO continues to lead industry standards with V-NAND technology for reliable and unrivaled performance. Accelerate into next-gen computing with read speeds up to 3. 200 TBW*. Experience the SSD that goes further. * Varies by capacity
